# Personal overlay (local, gitignored)

This file is your **personal overlay** for this Arbiter home base. It is
gitignored and never committed — anything here stays on this machine only.

Use it for local identity and preferences that should not be shared with
collaborators: a persona for the <%= @coordinator %> session, machine-specific
paths, private reminders, or any overrides to the doctrine in `CLAUDE.md`.

`CLAUDE.md` (the committed role doc) is loaded alongside this file, so
whatever you put here layers on top of it.

